Write a Java function to calculate the sum of the first n natural numbers.

Example:
Input: 5
Output: 15

import java.util.*;
class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int n = 5;
        System.out.println(sumOfNaturalNumbers(n));
    }
    public static int sumOfNaturalNumbers(int n){
        return n*(n+1)/2;
    }
}
